"*References: Vosselman, G. (2000): Slope based filtering of laser altimetry "
"data. IAPRS, Vol. XXXIII, Part B3, Amsterdam, The Netherlands, 935-942*"
msgstr ""
"*Verwijzingen: Vosselman, G. (2000): Slope based filtering of laser "
"altimetry data. IAPRS, Vol. XXXIII, Part B3, Amsterdam, The Netherlands, "
"935-942*"

