msgid "Fill sinks (Wang & Liu)"
msgstr "Fill sinks (Wang & Liu)"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:270
msgid "|344|"
msgstr "|344|"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:272
msgid ""
"Uses a method proposed by Wang & Liu to identify and fill surface "
"depressions in digital elevation models."
msgstr ""
"Gebruikt een methode die werd voorgesteld door Wang & Liu om verlagingen in "
"oppervlakten te identificeren en te vullen in digitale hoogtemodellen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:274
msgid ""
"The method was enhanced to allow the creation of hydrologically sound "
"elevation models, i.e. not only to fill the depression(s) but also to "
"preserve a downward slope along the flow path. If desired, this is "
"accomplished by preserving a minimum slope gradient (and thus elevation "
"difference) between cells."
msgstr ""
"De methode werd verbeterd om toe te staan om hydrologische hoogtemodellen "
"mogelijk te maken, d.i. niet alleen de verlaging(en) te vullen, maar ook om "
"een aflopende helling langs het stroompad te behouden. Indien gewenst wordt "
"dat bereikt door een minimaal hellingsverloop te behouden (en dus "
"hoogteverschil) tussen cellen."

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:278
msgid ""
"*References: Wang, L. & H. Liu (2006): An efficient method for identifying "
"and filling surface depressions in digital elevation models for hydrologic "
"analysis and modelling. International Journal of Geographical Information "
"Science, Vol. 20, No. 2: 193-213.*"
msgstr ""
"*Verwijzingen: Wang, L. & H. Liu (2006): An efficient method for identifying"
" and filling surface depressions in digital elevation models for hydrologic "
"analysis and modelling. International Journal of Geographical Information "
"Science, Vol. 20, No. 2: 193-213.*"

#: ../../docs/user_manual/processing_algs/qgis/rasterterrainanalysis.rst:282
msgid "This tool is a port of the SAGA `Fill Sinks (Wang & Liu)`_ tool."
msgstr ""
"Dit gereedschap is een port van het gereedschap voor SAGA `Fill Sinks (Wang "
"& Liu)`_."

